iStore South Africa has launched its Big Annual Sale, which will run from 23 May until 9 June 2019. The sale features discounts on a range of Apple products, including MacBooks, iPhones, Apple Watches, and accessories. Discounted products include the MacBook Pro 13-inch, iPhone Xr 64GB, Apple Watch Series 4, and new iPad Pro. The special deals are available in-store and online while stocks last. Sale discounts will also be applied at the iStore Factory Shop. The top deals from the sale are shown below. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-307182" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/MacBook-Air-from-iStore.jpg" alt="MacBook Air from iStore" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/MacBook-Air-from-iStore.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/MacBook-Air-from-iStore-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/MacBook-Air-from-iStore-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-307184" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/iPhone-Xr-from-iStore.jpg" alt="iPhone Xr from iStore" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/iPhone-Xr-from-iStore.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/iPhone-Xr-from-iStore-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/iPhone-Xr-from-iStore-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-307186" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/iPhone-8-from-iStore.jpg" alt="iPhone 8 from iStore" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/iPhone-8-fro